Name: flask-restful-routing
Version: 1.0.3
Summary: An easier way to register flask-restful routes
Home-page: https://github.com/twopicode/flask-restful-routing
Author: Nick Whyte
Author-email: nick@nickwhyte.com
License: UNKNOWN
Description: flask-restful-routing
        ============================================
        
        Installation
        ++++++++++++
        
          pip install marshmallow-sqlalchemy-referential
        
        Sample Usage
        ++++++++++++
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
          restful_api = Api(app)
          resources = RouteRoot([
              Route('login', '/login', Login),
              Route('search', '/search', Search),
              Route('document', '/documents', Documents, Document, [
                  Route('attachment', '/attachments', Attachments, Attachment)
              ])
          ])
          
          resources.register_routes(restful_api)
        
